<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Public Website | n8n Management</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-primary: #0f172a;
            --bg-secondary: #1e293b;
            --bg-card: #1e293b;
            --text-primary: #f1f5f9;
            --text-secondary: #94a3b8;
            --accent: #f97316;
            --accent-glow: rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.3);
            --border: #334155;
        }
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg-primary);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .bg-grid {
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            background-image:
                linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 60px 60px;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .bg-glow {
            position: fixed;
            width: 500px;
            height: 500px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            filter: blur(100px);
            opacity: 0.15;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .glow-1 { top: -150px; right: -150px; background: var(--accent); }
        .glow-2 { bottom: -150px; left: -150px; background: #3b82f6; }
        .container {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease-out;
        }
        @keyframes fadeUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        .logo {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            margin: 0 auto 2rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #ea580c);
            border-radius: 24px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px var(--accent-glow);
        }
        .logo svg {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            fill: white;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.25rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--text-primary), var(--text-secondary));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }
        .subtitle {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        }
        .card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .card-title {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }
        .card-title svg {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            fill: var(--accent);
        }
        .steps {
            list-style: none;
        }
        .steps li {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            padding: 0.75rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 1rem;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .steps li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .step-num {
            background: var(--accent);
            color: white;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: var(--accent);
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: var(--accent);
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="bg-grid"></div>
    <div class="bg-glow glow-1"></div>
    <div class="bg-glow glow-2"></div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 3H5c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm-7 14H6v-2h6v2zm4-4H6v-2h10v2zm0-4H6V7h10v2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h1>Public Website Ready</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">This is your public-facing website. To customize it with your own content, use the File Browser in the management console.</p>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-title">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2L4 5v6.09c0 5.05 3.41 9.76 8 10.91 4.59-1.15 8-5.86 8-10.91V5l-8-3zm-1 15h2v2h-2v-2zm0-8h2v6h-2V9z"/></svg>
                How to Upload Content
            </div>
            <ol class="steps">
                <li><span class="step-num">1</span><span>Navigate to your <span class="highlight">n8n Management Console</span></span></li>
                <li><span class="step-num">2</span><span>Log in with your admin credentials</span></li>
                <li><span class="step-num">3</span><span>Click on <span class="highlight">Files</span> in the sidebar</span></li>
                <li><span class="step-num">4</span><span>Upload or edit files to replace this page</span></li>
            </ol>
        </div>
        <p class="footer">Powered by <a href="https://github.com/rjsears/n8n_nginx" target="_blank">n8n Management</a></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
